detaileddescription.para: Object initialization has finished and it is now in the 'runtime' stage. This affects e.g. what options can be set on the object (only AV_OPT_FLAG_RUNTIME_PARAM options can be set on initialized objects).
Describe the class of an AVClass context structure. That is an arbitrary struct of which the first field is a pointer to an AVClass struct (e.g. AVCodecContext, AVFormatContext etc.).
